</a>&#160;(15–20)</span>\n</td>\n<td>2% chance\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Maple Syrup.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/6a/Maple_Syrup.png/24px-Maple_Syrup.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/6a/Maple_Syrup.png/36px-Maple_Syrup.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/6/6a/Maple_Syrup.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Maple_Syrup\" title=\"Maple Syrup\">Maple Syrup</a></span>\n</td>\n<td>0.66% chance\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Oak Resin.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/40/Oak_Resin.png/24px-Oak_Resin.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/40/Oak_Resin.png/36px-Oak_Resin.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/4/40/Oak_Resin.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Oak_Resin\" title=\"Oak Resin\">Oak Resin</a></span>\n</td>\n<td>0.66% chance\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Pine Tar.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/ce/Pine_Tar.png/24px-Pine_Tar.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/ce/Pine_Tar.png/36px-Pine_Tar.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/c/ce/Pine_Tar.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Pine_Tar\" title=\"Pine Tar\">Pine Tar</a></span>\n</td>\n<td>0.66% chance\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Driftwood.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/63/Driftwood.png/24px-Driftwood.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/63/Driftwood.png/36px-Driftwood.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/6/63/Driftwood.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Driftwood\" title=\"Driftwood\">Driftwood</a>&#160;(1)</span>\n</td>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Wood.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/df/Wood.png/24px-Wood.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/df/Wood.png/36px-Wood.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/d/df/Wood.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Wood\" title=\"Wood\">Wood</a>&#160;(5–10)</span>\n</td>\n<td>100% chance\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Wood_Chipper&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: History\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.4\" title=\"Version History\">1.4</a>: Introduced.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.6\" title=\"Version History\">1.6</a>: Now obtainable from <a href=\"/Desert_Festival\" title=\"Desert Festival\">Desert Festival</a>.</li></ul>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" id=\"navbox\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"3\">Equipment\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/Crafting#Artisan_Equipment\" title=\"Crafting\">Artisan</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Bee_House\" title=\"Bee House\">Bee House</a> • <a href=\"/Cask\" title=\"Cask\">Cask</a> • <a href=\"/Cheese_Press\" title=\"Cheese Press\">Cheese Press</a> • <a href=\"/Dehydrator\" title=\"Dehydrator\">Dehydrator</a> • <a href=\"/Fish_Smoker\" title=\"Fish Smoker\">Fish Smoker</a> • <a href=\"/Keg\" title=\"Keg\">Keg</a> • <a href=\"/Loom\" title=\"Loom\">Loom</a> • <a href=\"/Mayonnaise_Machine\" title=\"Mayonnaise Machine\">Mayonnaise Machine</a> • <a href=\"/Oil_Maker\" title=\"Oil Maker\">Oil Maker</a> • <a href=\"/Preserves_Jar\" title=\"Preserves Jar\">Preserves Jar</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/Crafting#Refining_Equipment\" title=\"Crafting\">Refining</a>\n</