      "wikitext": "{{Infobox\n|eng         = Wood Chipper\n|image2      = Wood Chipper On\n|image2spacing = true\n|source      = [[Carpenter's Shop]] for {{Price|1000}}\n|sellprice   = N/A\n}}\nThe '''Wood Chipper''' is used to convert [[Hardwood]] and [[Driftwood]] into other products. It can be purchased from the [[Carpenter's Shop]] for {{Price|1000}} starting the first day of [[Winter]] in year 1. The player receives a letter about the wood chipper from [[Robin]] on the second day of Winter in year 1. A Wood Chipper may be purchased from [[Kent]]'s [[Desert Festival#Villager Shops|shop]] at the [[Desert Festival]] for {{Price|25|Calico}} [[Calico Egg]]s.\n\n==Products==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable roundedborder\"\n! Input\n!colspan=\"2\"| Outputs One Of\n! Processing Time\n|-\n|rowspan=\"5\"| {{name|Hardwood|1}}\n| {{name|Wood|5–10}}\n| 96% chance\n|rowspan=\"6\"| {{Duration|180mins (3hrs)}}\n|-\n| {{name|Wood|15–20}}\n| 2% chance\n|-\n| {{name|Maple Syrup}}\n| 0.66% chance\n|-\n| {{name|Oak Resin}}\n| 0.66% chance\n|-\n| {{name|Pine Tar}}\n| 0.66% chance\n|-\n| {{name|Driftwood|1}}\n| {{name|Wood|5–10}}\n| 100% chance\n|}\n\n==History==\n{{History|1.4|Introduced.}}\n{{History|1.6|Now obtainable from [[Desert Festival]].}}\n\n{{NavboxEquipment}}\n\n[[Category:Special items]]\n\n[[de:Holzhackmaschine]]\n[[es:Astilladora]]\n[[fr:Déchiqueteuse de bois]]\n[[it:Cippatrice]]\n[[ja:ウッドチッパー]]\n[[ko:목재파쇄기]]\n[[hu:Fadaráló]]\n[[pt:Triturador de Madeira]]\n[[ru:Дробилка]]\n[[tr:Ağaç Öğütücü]]\n[[zh:碎木机]]"
